</td></tr></table></div><div style='margin-left: 5px'>Before you even start talking about how you would change things to reduce the incidence of spree shootings, you are going to have to say something about the biggest elephant: spree shootings are very rare, and nearly all child deaths come from other, much bigger causes, so it's far from clear that this problem deserves more than a mote of our limited time, attention and resources.</div><div style='margin-top: 3px; font-size: smaller'><span class='commentlinks'>(<a href="http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?replyto=3676734" rel="nofollow">Reply</a>) </span>(<a href='http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3676734#t3676734'>Thread</a>) <div class="quickreply" id="ljqrt3676734" style="display: none;"></div></div></div><div style='margin-left: 25px;margin-top:5px;' id="ljcmt3676990" class="ljcmt_full">
