</td></tr></table></div><div style='margin-left: 5px'>3.4 percent of children by gun related deaths is still way too high.i am amazed you don't feel so.</div><div style='margin-top: 3px; font-size: smaller'><span class='commentlinks'>(<a href="http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?replyto=3687230" rel="nofollow">Reply</a>) </span>(<a href='http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3682110#t3682110'>Parent</a>) (<a href='http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3687230#t3687230'>Thread</a>) <span id='expand_3687230'>(<a href='http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3687230#t3687230' onclick="ExpanderEx.make(event,this,'http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3687230#t3687230','3687230',true)">Expand</a>)</span><div class="quickreply" id="ljqrt3687230" style="display: none;"></div></div></div><div style='margin-left: 50px;margin-top:5px;' id="ljcmt3687742">
