<a name='t3685182'></a><div id='cmtbar3685182' style='background-color: #dddddd; color: #000000; margin-top: 10px; width: 100%;'><table border='0' cellpadding='2' cellspacing='0' summary='0' style='width: 100%'><tr valign='top'><td style='width: 102px'><img src='http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/34040520/5505369' width='100' height='100' alt='[User Picture]' /></td><td style='width: 50%'><strong>From:</strong> <span  class="ljuser  i-ljuser     "  lj:user="st_rev"><a href="http://st-rev.livejournal.com/profile" ><img width="16" height="16"  class="i-ljuser-userhead"  src="http://l-stat.livejournal.com/img/userinfo.gif?v=100" /></a><a href="http://st-rev.livejournal.com/" class="i-ljuser-username"   ><b>st_rev</b></a></span><br /><small><span title="6 hours after journal entry">2012-12-22 04:27 pm (UTC)</span></small><br /><h3> Re: dk</h3></td><td align='right' style='width: 50%'>                <p><strong>(<a href='http://squid314.livejournal.com/347454.html?thread=3685182#t3685182'>Link</a>)</strong></p>
